<div class="vacancyWrapper">
    <div class="row bPad40 clearFix">
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-12 rPad40">
            <h3 class="subtitle sans hasBorder">We want to hear from you</h3>
            <p>25 June 2018</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="maxWidth480 cmsContent">
                <p>We are always happy to hear from talented, experienced, friendly, ambitious professionals who are interested in joining the Wish team. If that&#8217;s you, please drop us a mail at <a href="http://www.wishstudios.co.uk/mailto:jobs@wishstudios.co.uk">jobs@wishstudios.co.uk</a> with a few details about you, and a copy of your CV and resume.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
